## Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User] --> B[user_roles table]
    B --> C[roles table]
    C --> D[role_permissions table]
    D --> E[permissions table]

    B --> F{Role Assignment}
    F -->|admin| G[Platform Admin<br/>Full access]
    F -->|school-admin| H[School Admin<br/>School-scoped]
    F -->|teacher| I[Teacher<br/>Class-scoped]
    F -->|student| J[Student<br/>Own data only]
    F -->|parent| K[Parent<br/>Children data]
    F -->|counselor| L[Counselor<br/>Student data]
    F -->|ministry| M[Ministry<br/>National view]

    style G fill:#ec4899
    style H fill:#8b5cf6
    style I fill:#3b82f6
    style J fill:#f97316
    style K fill:#9ca3af
    style L fill:#a855f7
    style M fill:#6366f1
```

**RBAC Tables:**
1. `roles` - Role definitions
2. `permissions` - Permission definitions
3. `user_roles` - User-role assignments
4. `role_permissions` - Role-permission mapping

**Default Roles:**
| Role | Description | Permissions |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| admin | Platform administrator | Full system access |
| school-admin | School administrator | School-scoped access |
| teacher | Teacher | Class/subject access |
| student | Student | Own data access |
| parent | Parent | Children data access |
| counselor | Counselor | Student support access |
| ministry | Ministry official | National view access |

