## Portal Authentication Pattern

All 7 portals use the same authentication pattern in their layout:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Portal Layout Component] --> B[useEffect on mount]
    B --> C[Fetch /api/auth/set-role]
    C --> D[Fetch /api/user/profile]

    D --> E{Response check}
    E -->|needsSetup: true| F[Set needsSetup state]
    E -->|userType exists| G[Set userType state]

    F --> H[Redirect to /setup/unified]
    G --> I[Render Portal Sidebar]
    I --> J[Render Children]

    style F fill:#fff3cd
    style H fill:#fef3c7
    style I fill:#d4edda
```

**Layout Files:**
1. `src/app/[portal]/layout.tsx` - Dynamic portal routing
2. `src/app/admin/layout.tsx` - Admin-specific (bypass setup)
3. `src/app/parent/layout.tsx` - Parent-specific

