## Authorization Matrix

| Resource | Admin | School Admin | Teacher | Student | Parent | Counselor | Ministry |
|----------|-------|-------------|---------|---------|--------|-----------|----------|
| Users (all) | ✅ RW | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ R |
| Schools (all) | ✅ RW | ✅ R (own) | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ R |
| Students (all) | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ R (class) | ✅ R (self) | ✅ R (children) | ✅ R (assigned) | ✅ R |
| Teachers (all) | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ R (self) | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ R |
| Classes (all) | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ RW (assigned) | ✅ R (own) | ✅ R (children) | ❌ | ❌ |
| Homework | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ RW (assigned) | ✅ RW (own) | ✅ R (children) | ❌ | ❌ |
| Assessments | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ RW (assigned) | ✅ R (own) | ✅ R (children) | ✅ R (assigned) | ❌ |
| Attendance | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ RW (assigned) | ✅ R (own) | ✅ R (children) | ✅ R (assigned) | ❌ |
| Fees | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ❌ | ✅ R (self) | ✅ RW (children) | ❌ | ❌ |
| Reports | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ✅ R (class) | ✅ R (self) | ✅ R (children) | ✅ R (assigned) | ✅ R (national) |
| Settings | ✅ RW | ✅ RW (school) | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ RW |
| Billing | ✅ RW | ✅ R (own) | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ R |

**Legend:**
- ✅ R = Read access
- ✅ RW = Read + Write access
- ❌ = No access
- (school) = School-scoped only
- (own) = Own data only
- (children) = Children data only
- (class) = Assigned classes only
- (assigned) = Assigned students only
- (national) = National-level data

