## Session Management

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Clerk
    participant Middleware
    participant API as API Route
    participant DB as Database

    User->>Clerk: Sign in
    Clerk-->>User: Session token
    User->>Middleware: Request with token
    Middleware->>Clerk: Verify token
    Clerk-->>Middleware: User data
    Middleware->>API: Forward request
    API->>DB: Query with clerkUserId
    DB-->>API: User record
    API-->>User: Response

    Note over User,DB: All subsequent requests<br/>include Clerk session token
```

